sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant FastAPI
    participant MinIO
    participant Celery
    participant PostgreSQL
    participant Weaviate
    
    Client->>FastAPI: POST /ingest/document (file upload)
    FastAPI->>MinIO: Store document
    FastAPI->>PostgreSQL: Save metadata
    FastAPI->>Celery: Queue chunking task
    Celery->>MinIO: Read document
    Celery->>Celery: Chunk text (recursive/semantic)
    Celery->>Weaviate: Create vector embeddings
    Celery->>PostgreSQL: Update chunk metadata
    Celery->>FastAPI: Task completion callback